mindmap
  root((Desktop POS System))
    Authentication Module
      Login Process
        UI: Form nhập liệu
        Action: Validate Input
        API: POST /api/auth/login
      Session Management
        Store JWT Token
        Auto-attach Token to Headers
        Logout / Session Expiry Handling

    Table Management Module
      Table Visualizer
        Load Table List (GET /api/tables)
        Render Layout (Floor 1 / Floor 2)
        Color Coding (Green=Empty, Red=Occupied)
      Real-time Sync
        SignalR Connection
        Event: Receive 'TableUpdated'
        Action: Refresh Table UI
      Table Operations
        Select Table
        View Table Details

    Order Processing Module
      Menu Catalog
        Load Categories (GET /api/categories)
        Load Products (GET /api/products)
        Search & Filter
      Shopping Cart (Local State)
        Add Item to Cart
        Update Quantity
        Remove Item
        Add Item Notes
      Order Submission
        Validate Cart
        API: POST /api/orders (New Order)
        API: PUT /api/orders/{id} (Update Order)
        Handle Success/Error Response

    Payment Module
      Checkout Process
        Calculate Total
        Select Payment Method
      QR Payment
        Action: Get Bank Info
        API: GET /api/payment-settings
        Generate QR Code (VietQR)
      Transaction Finalization
        API: POST /api/orders/{id}/pay
        Update Local Status
        Print Receipt (Optional)

    Reporting Module
      Dashboard Stats
        Load Daily Sales (GET /api/reports)
        Render Charts (LiveCharts)
        Top Selling Products
      Data Export
        Export Orders to CSV
        Export Revenue Report
        Save File Dialog

    System Configuration
      Connection Settings
        API Base URL
      Payment Configuration
        Update Bank Info (Admin)
        API: PUT /api/payment-settings
